high_descs: Go straight to face the brown shelf in the corner.
Pick the sponge up from off of the shelf.
Turn around then go to the left to face the counter.
Place the sponge inside of the pan.
Pick up the pan from off of the counter.
Move to the right to face the cabinet below the sink.
Place the pan in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place the pan with the sponge in the cabinet under the sink.

high_descs: Head to the shelf across the kitchen
Take the green sponge from the shelf
Turn around, head to the counter
Put the green sponge in the pan on the counter
Turn around, head to the sink
Open the cabinet door under the sink
Put the pan in the cabinet
anns.task_desc: Put the green sponge and pan under the sink

high_descs: Move to the brown shelving unit in the corner.
Pick up the green sponge from the second shelf.
Carry the sponge to the counter space directly to the left of the stove.
Place the sponge in the round pan.
Pick up the pan with the sponge inside from the counter.
Carry the pan and sponge to the kitchen sink.
Open the cupboards beneath the sink and place the pan and sponge inside.
anns.task_desc: Move a pan with a sponge inside to a cupboard beneath the sink.
